treated 1.035 |-------|                      6.679
control 1.173 |---------------------------| 17.954

- Units with the 5 most extreme weights by group:

           5290   2274   2032   2026   1924
 treated  5.909  5.954  6.183  6.509  6.679
           2512   2444   1463   1420   1221
 control 13.951 14.289 16.605 17.492 17.954

- Weight statistics:

