## Business Interpretation

::: {.callout-note}
**Steering delivers the most value for glass and body damage claims.** Engine damage shows
moderate benefits. For total loss, steering provides no cost advantage — resources should
focus on quality (CSAT) and speed rather than cost optimisation in this segment.
:::


